1.	List files - ls 
hdfs dfs -ls / 
 
2.	Make dir hdfs dfs -mkdir /techcoreeasy 
 
3.	create empty file hdfs dfs -touchz /techcoreeasy/test1.txt 
 
4.	cp file from local file system to hdfs 
hdfs dfs -put tech.txt /techcoreeasy/ 
 
5.	see contents - cat hdfs dfs -cat /techcoreeasy/tech.txt 
 
6.	copy - cp hdfs dfs -cp /techcoreeasy /test_cp 
 
7.	get file to local hdfs dfs -get /techcoreeasy/test.txt . 
 
8.	Remove file hdfs dfs -rmr /techcoreeasy/test.txt 
 
9.	stst of a file 
hdfs dfs -stat /path 
 
10.	exit command, switch from bash mode to command prompt  
 
